	* semaphore.c: Handle spurious wakeups.

	* sysdeps/pthread/pthread.h: Add back PTHREAD_MUTX_FAST_NP as an alias
	for PTHREAD_MUTEX_ADAPTIVE_NP for source code compatibility.

