	* manager.c (pthread_allocate_stack): Handle
	NEED_SEPARATE_REGISTER_STACK.
	(pthread_handle_create): Likewise.
	* pthread.c (__pthread_initialize_manager): Likewise.

	* sysdeps/ia64/pt-machine.h: Use r13 for thread pointer.

